===Alternative forms===
* {{alter|en|vermillion}} (more at [[vermillion#Usage notes|vermillion § Usage notes]])

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|fro|vermeillon|t=vermilion}}, from {{m|fro|vermeil}}, from {{der|en|la|vermiculus|t=little worm}}, from {{m|la|vermis|t=worm}}, ultimately in reference to {{taxlink|Kermes vermilio|species|noshow=1}}, a type of scale insect used to make a crimson dye.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/vɜː(ɹ)ˈmɪl.jən/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɪljən|lang=en}}

